==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: mooch
<hw>mooch</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>to ask for and get
free; to borrow without intending to repay; to sponge; -- usually with
objects of small value; <as>as, he <ex>mooched</ex> a few cigarettes
from me</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bum, cadge, grub, sponge.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To beg for.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>moo-cow</ent>⟦br⟧
